    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk the doctor is so expensive and it's a hassle. if i just drink like a ton of water and maybe take some extra ibuprofen for the nausea it'll probably be fine right? it's probably just my body adjusting to the med since i recently changed my routine. u think i can just wait a week to see if it goes away?",
